 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Garmin adds watchfaces and more apps to its app store", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-08-06T18:30:00+00:00", "description": "<figure>\n      <img alt=\"The Google search bar getting smashed by a gavel\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Uk8RbA0fIzYfo3nwiIjiWDKRnHY=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73505252/236780_Google_AntiTrust_Trial_Custom_Art_CVirginia__0002_2.0.png\" />\n        <figcaption>Illustration by Cath Virginia / The Verge</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n\n  \t\t <p>Finally, a legal ruling on whether TikTok is a real search engine. (It\u2019s not.)</p>\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/24214574/google-antitrust-search-apple-microsoft-bing-ruling-breakdown\">Continue reading&hellip;</a>\n  </p>", "id": 986288, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.theverge.com/24214574/google-antitrust-search-apple-microsoft-bing-ruling-breakdown", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "source_obj__id": 359, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "\u2018There\u2019s no price\u2019 Microsoft could pay Apple to use Bing: all the spiciest parts of the Google antitrust ruling", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-08-06T18:05:11+00:00", "description": "<figure>\n      <img alt=\"A screenshot of the video game Star Wars Jedi: Survivor.\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tHuIjg86-ZQcxkv5zkWPAeVAatk=/129x269:2582x1904/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73505199/Cal_and_BD_1_seek_out_a_safe_haven.0.png\" />\n        <figcaption><em>Cal Kestis returns to his last-gen roots soon.</em> | Image: EA</figc